title: **1 MONTH FREE! BRAND NEW Studio, Floor to Ceiling Windows, Patio!
posting_body: ['Embrace Convenience', 'OME is a new boutique SoMa community, offering modern, well-designed, highly efficient apartments.', 'Designed by local David Baker Architects , OME has been created for you.', 'This unit has a well thought out open floorplan, lots of built in storage and lighting.', 'Brand new building, modern interior, quiet unit (thick walls)', 'Private Patio!', '1 MONTH FREE!', 'Community Amenities', '- Community Room', '- Barbeque', '- Laundry Onsite', '- Roof Deck', '- Bike Room', '- Package Room', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed, Small dogs allowed', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday-Saturday:9:00AM-4:00PM', 'OME Apartments', '663 Clementina St., San Francisco, CA, 94103', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'AMC-CA, Inc. dba Apartment Management Consultants-BRE #01525033', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
